proceed to gate one.

00:52.636 --> 00:56.220
-Await further instructions.
GUARD: Copy, Miss Pe/ham.

00:58.141 --> 01:01.053
Well done, dog.

01:01.645 --> 01:03.226
[IN SPANISH]
What next, madame?

01:04.064 --> 01:05.975
