The road is a quarter mile off.

01:35.178 --> 01:38.261
MARNIE [IN ENGLISH]:
Relay this message to your king.

01:38.432 --> 01:41.845
It is Antonia Gavilan de Logroﬁo.

01:42.019 --> 01:44.351
