for a real-life vamp attack video.

04:03.493 --> 04:07.327
VONETTA: You'll have to share it with me.
CORALEE: What's the matter with her face?

04:07.497 --> 04:10.830
-Hey. Show us your face.
CORALEE: Are you sure she ain't a zombie?

04:11.001 --> 04:13.083
VONETTA:
Holy crap. Now there's zombies?

04:13.253 --> 04:16.666
I am not a zombie.

04:16.840 --> 04:20.332
CORALEE: That's exactly what a zombie
would say, "I'm not a zombie."

04:20.552 --> 04:21.758
Like she's gonna tell us.

04:21.928 --> 04:25.045
It may be 10 minutes from now
or 10 years.

04:25.766 --> 04:27.506
The moment you think you're safe...

04:27.684 --> 04:32.678
...I promise I will hunt you down
and fucking shred you like confetti.

04:35.692 --> 04:37.432
CORALEE: I ain't getting--
VONETTA: Should we go help?

04:37.611 --> 04:41.820
Bartolo. I swear to God, l'll burn
this fucking taco stand to the ground...

04:41.990 --> 04:44.197
...if you don't let us up
out this motherfucker.

04:44.367 --> 04:45.618
You fucking hear me?

04:49.998 --> 04:51.204
BARTOLO:
What?

04:51.374 --> 04:53.205
l was fucking my wife.

04:53.877 --> 04:55.833
We need to go home.

04:57.547 --> 05:00.084
I'm a grown man now, Abuelito.

05:01.218 --> 05:04.051
And I refuse to become
what you want me to be.

05:04.221 --> 05:07.634
Now either you're too stubborn
or you're too fucking stupid to see that.

05:07.808 --> 05:12.051
-You sick fuck. You almost killed him.
-Your own son.

05:12.229 --> 05:15.392
Tio Luca came back to this shithole
just to save me.

05:16.191 --> 05:19.058
At least somebody in this family cares
whether or not I die.

05:19.236 --> 05:21.101
BARTOLO:
Luca?

05:21.571 --> 05:23.402
How did he get here?

05:23.573 --> 05:26.736
That pendejo's been dead 10 years.

05:26.910 --> 05:29.071
How did he get here?

05:29.246 --> 05:31.157
I'm not a fucking idiot.

05:31.331 --> 05:33.572
-He's a medium.
-Wait, me?

05:33.750 --> 05:37.242
But what I don't get
is how you can risk my life...

05:37.420 --> 05:39.001
...just to prove your point.

05:39.172 --> 05:41.254
Don't be so dramatic.

05:41.424 --> 05:43.585
I wouldn't sacrifice you.

05:43.760 --> 05:45.341
You're the last of us left.

05:47.097 --> 05:49.053
Wait, can we go back
to how I'm a medium?

05:49.224 --> 05:51.340
He's so smart, let him explain it to you.

05:51.518 --> 05:54.100
What the genius doesn't understand...

05:54.271 --> 05:56.353
...is I didn't have to prove nothing
to him.

05:57.065 --> 05:58.680
I had to prove it to you.

06:01.278 --> 06:03.109
[IN SPANISH]
You have the magic.

06:10.787 --> 06:13.779
Well, you could've just fucking said so.

06:24.259 --> 06:25.374
Debbie Pelt...

06:27.053 --> 06:30.295
...you are our sister.

06:32.809 --> 06:38.429
Alcide Herveaux, you are our brother.

06:39.816 --> 06:42.432
We welcome you into our land...

06:42.611 --> 06:46.149
...and call upon you to defend it with us.

06:46.573 --> 06:49.280
[ALL WHOOPING]

06:52.829 --> 06:54.194
MAN: Yeah.
WOMAN: Yeah!

06:58.960 --> 07:01.667
[ROCK MUSIC PLAYING
& PEOPLE CHATTERING]

07:04.799 --> 07:06.175
Hey.

07:13.808 --> 07:16.345
