07:17.020 --> 07:19.102
SooMe.

07:19.272 --> 07:21.513
It's the woods on a full moon, babe.

07:21.691 --> 07:25.183
You know what all's out here.
It ain't right to just leave her alone.

07:25.362 --> 07:29.025
