07:39.709 --> 07:41.210
Come on.

07:43.713 --> 07:46.125
Wait. Hold on.

07:48.009 --> 07:50.386
We can spare 10 minutes to look.

07:57.686 --> 07:59.677
[SNIFFS]

08:01.856 --> 08:03.357
You smell her?

08:03.525 --> 08:05.061
Can't you?

08:06.736 --> 08:09.398
