08:54.117 --> 08:56.699
I need a word, Your Majesty.

08:57.454 --> 08:58.819
Is it our prisoner?

09:00.749 --> 09:05.288
l was sent with a message
from Antonia Gavilan de Logroﬁo.

09:05.462 --> 09:07.293
Logrono?

09:07.464 --> 09:09.955
