-All things are possible.

09:14.929 --> 09:16.089
[SCREAMS]

09:18.558 --> 09:21.174
[GRUNTING]

09:24.230 --> 09:26.061
What is your business with Antonia?

09:27.150 --> 09:29.357
Where is she? Answer me?

09:34.074 --> 09:36.736
[IN SPANISH]
Resurrection.

09:54.177 --> 09:56.509
-Put on your seat belt.
-I can't.

09:57.847 --> 10:00.008
-Put it on and we can go.
-I can't go with you.

10:00.183 --> 10:01.673
-Toni. Don't be so--
-Tara.

10:04.354 --> 10:05.844
I changed my mind.

10:06.022 --> 10:07.262
I don't like Tara.

10:07.440 --> 10:10.773
