says you don't really like her either.

10:10.944 --> 10:12.480
Fuck her. Let's go.

10:12.654 --> 10:16.863
We just came within a fingernail
of getting eaten by a vampire...

10:17.033 --> 10:21.197
...one who swears she's coming back
for more. There ain't no place to go.

10:26.668 --> 10:31.458
Everyone who's ever been with me
has ended up dead.

10:31.631 --> 10:33.963
It ain't a long list...

10:34.134 --> 10:36.045
...but it's a bad one to be on.

10:36.219 --> 10:38.881
-Can I please choose what happens to me?
-I can't.

10:39.055 --> 10:41.387
-Your blood's gonna end up on my hands.
-|t's not.

10:41.558 --> 10:44.800
They're gonna get me. If it ain't
this vampire, it's gonna be another.

10:44.978 --> 10:47.560
If you don't get up out of here,
you're dying with me.

10:47.730 --> 10:50.392
I'm barely hanging on to my own life.

10:52.902 --> 10:56.235
I do not want to be responsible
for yours too.

10:56.406 --> 10:59.489
I'm asking to stay
because I care about you.

11:00.743 --> 11:03.735
Tell me that doesn't count for anything.

11:07.584 --> 11:08.915
Not enough.

11:14.215 --> 11:16.752
-You know you're gonna regret this.
-I already do.

11:16.968 --> 11:19.004
Now fucking drive.

11:27.103 --> 11:28.843
[CAR ENGINE STARTS]

11:39.449 --> 11:41.405
[SOBBING]

11:53.254 --> 11:55.245
[GRUNTING]

11:55.548 --> 11:57.129
Jason.

11:58.801 --> 12:00.883
[PANTING]

12:08.061 --> 12:09.141
[DOORBELL RINGS]

12:09.312 --> 12:10.472
Oh, Shit.

12:12.649 --> 12:14.139
Stay calm.

12:14.317 --> 12:15.853
Don't do nothing.

12:16.027 --> 12:17.233
[DOORBELL RINGS]

12:17.737 --> 12:19.238
Fuck.

12:22.659 --> 12:24.149
Listen, you gotta--

12:24.327 --> 12:26.659
Hey, bubba.

12:26.829 --> 12:29.161
-What's up?
-Just checking in on you.

12:31.334 --> 12:33.495
You weren't answering your phone.

12:33.962 --> 12:36.544
Yeah. Must have left it.

12:36.965 --> 12:38.000
Jess ain't with you?

12:38.174 --> 12:41.507
Uh, Vampire Bill needed her for something,
she said.

12:41.678 --> 12:44.010
So she's staying there tonight.

12:44.180 --> 12:47.092
Oh. Okay.

12:47.267 --> 12:49.508
That ain't nothing for you to worry about.

12:49.686 --> 12:50.846
You can trust her.

12:51.020 --> 12:53.352
-Yeah, everyone says that.
-Totally trust her.

12:55.191 --> 12:57.182
It's you I'm worried about.

12:58.319 --> 13:00.856
Why? What?

13:01.072 --> 13:02.357
-What did I do?
-J.

13:04.367 --> 13:05.857
You were raped.

13:08.037 --> 13:12.531
Yeah, and maybe turn
into a werewolf panther.

13:12.709 --> 13:14.870
It's just a were-panther.

13:15.044 --> 13:16.545
And I'm not.

13:16.713 --> 13:18.544
It was full moon.

13:18.715 --> 13:22.549
Nothing happened,
so I'm pretty sure I'm fine.

13:22.719 --> 13:27.634
-Well, it must be a relief at least, right?
-Yup. I'm cool.

13:27.807 --> 13:30.970
Don't you even think about me.

13:31.144 --> 13:32.680
Well....

13:33.730 --> 13:35.561
Yeah, I'm glad you're good.

13:38.109 --> 13:42.193
So you two ain't fixed things up yet?

13:42.363 --> 13:45.651
She's slipping away from me. I know it.

13:47.618 --> 13:51.076
Hey, you hungry?
I could make us Sloppy Joes.

13:51.247 --> 13:54.159
Sure. I mean,
if it's not too much trouble.

13:54.334 --> 13:57.576
Hell, it's no trouble at all.

13:57.754 --> 14:00.917
I mean, I'd rather be cooking
than talking anyhow.

14:01.090 --> 14:02.921
-|'m a good cook.
-Jason?

14:03.092 --> 14:06.004
-Yeah?
-I can't lose her.

14:06.179 --> 14:08.420
It'll kill me ifl lose her.

14:11.434 --> 14:13.140
Right. Two coming up.

14:14.020 --> 14:17.683
Who the hell
is Antonia Gavilan de Logroﬁo?

14:20.401 --> 14:24.110
She was the only human ever known
to wield power over vampires.

14:26.908 --> 14:30.446
-Was?
-She died 400 years ago.

14:33.289 --> 14:36.702
During the Spanish Inquisition,
vampires exploited the chaos...

14:36.876 --> 14:41.540
...by satiating their appetites
for blood and for lust.

14:41.714 --> 14:44.296
And one of their victims was Antonia.

14:44.467 --> 14:46.458
But she was a powerful necromancer.

14:46.636 --> 14:48.797
She could control the dead...

14:48.971 --> 14:51.462
...and as she burnt upon the stake,
she cast a spell...

14:51.682 --> 14:56.551
...that drew all of the vampires of Legrono
out into the sun.

14:56.729 --> 14:58.685
Holy fuck.

14:59.565 --> 15:03.274
-For real?
-I thought she was lost to the past.

15:03.444 --> 15:06.311
Cautionary lesson from our history.

15:06.489 --> 15:10.323
But I could see her influence on Luis.

15:11.619 --> 15:13.325
I felt it.

15:13.996 --> 15:15.497
She's returned.

15:15.665 --> 15:17.405
You mean, like a ghost?

15:20.336 --> 15:24.079
She's harmless on her own,
but somehow...

15:24.257 --> 15:26.498
...Antonia has inhabited Marnie's body...

15:27.510 --> 15:33.176
...and now that Antonia has a human host,
well, you can see the result.

15:33.349 --> 15:35.431
Well, why would Antonia want
to kill you?

15:35.601 --> 15:37.102
It's not just me.

15:38.312 --> 15:41.520
Luis promised resurrection.

15:42.358 --> 15:46.647
I believe that she wants
to make all vampires meet the sun.

15:47.697 --> 15:51.064
-Finish what she started in 1610.
-But that--

15:51.242 --> 15:53.358
That's insane.
There are millions of vampires.

15:53.536 --> 15:55.527
Since when has any fanatic
been held back...

15:55.746 --> 15:59.739
...by the improbability
of their righteous mission?

16:00.877 --> 16:02.538
Okay.

16:03.546 --> 16:06.128
Well, I sure as hell don't want
to fry in the sun.

16:06.299 --> 16:07.880
What do we do?

16:08.676 --> 16:11.964
BILL:
Sheriffs, alert every vampire in your area.

16:12.138 --> 16:15.722
Instruct them to leave the state.
I will handle areas three and five myself.

16:15.892 --> 16:19.555
Those who choose to stay,
they will do as we do.

16:20.688 --> 16:24.397
Bind ourselves with silver
to keep us in our coffins.

16:25.067 --> 16:28.230
You want us to willfully silver ourselves?

16:28.404 --> 16:31.237
I shall not abandon this kingdom,
and neither will you.

16:31.407 --> 16:36.197
The suffering will be great,
but it is our only chance to survive the day.

16:36.370 --> 16:39.737
Physical strength is our greatest asset,
and you wish us to surrender it?

16:39.916 --> 16:41.577
My decision is final.

16:41.751 --> 16:47.917
I will not expose my subjects
to another massacre like Legrono.

16:48.090 --> 16:51.332
So tonight we go to ground in silver.

16:52.720 --> 16:53.926
And then what?

16:54.096 --> 16:55.882
We brace...

16:57.266 --> 16:59.177
...for the resurrection.

17:02.688 --> 17:05.225
[MOANING]

17:31.133 --> 17:34.261
We left our clothes in the woods.

17:34.804 --> 17:36.465
You want me to go get them?

17:36.639 --> 17:39.096
Don't you dare move.

17:45.856 --> 17:47.312
You still there?

17:47.483 --> 17:49.815
I'm listening to your heartbeat.

17:51.404 --> 17:53.440
I can feel it.

17:53.614 --> 17:55.650
Every pulse.

17:56.158 --> 17:59.241
Through your skin into mine.

18:03.165 --> 18:06.498
If I lay still
and think about nothing else...

18:09.839 --> 18:12.501
...it feels like my own heart is beating.

18:14.510 --> 18:17.502
I feel like mine's still racing.

18:18.180 --> 18:21.343
At least there's some things
you haven't forgot.

18:29.191 --> 18:30.692
SooMe.

18:35.114 --> 18:36.900
Do you want me to remember again?

18:37.867 --> 18:40.028
Stop it. Of course I do.

18:40.202 --> 18:43.865
I mean,
I wouldn't want you to change any...

18:44.373 --> 18:46.864
...but I do want you
to get your memories back.

18:47.043 --> 18:49.034
Yeah, but that would change me.

18:50.171 --> 18:52.457
Once I know who I am...

18:53.549 --> 18:55.790
...everything I've done...

18:57.219 --> 18:59.961
...I couldn't possibly be the same.

19:00.139 --> 19:02.346
Would you still want me then?

19:09.190 --> 19:11.476
I don't know.

19:13.736 --> 19:20.403
You did a lot of terrible things
to me and people I love.

19:20.576 --> 19:26.492
But then there's the you
who's so good and kind and sweet.

19:26.666 --> 19:29.078
I'd never have let the old you
into my bed.

19:29.251 --> 19:31.742
God knows you tried.

19:33.339 --> 19:36.581
Sookie, would you still want me?

19:36.759 --> 19:39.250
I hope I would.

19:40.388 --> 19:42.925
I hope I will.

19:44.433 --> 19:45.969
Because”.

19:46.769 --> 19:49.511
...that day is gonna come...

19:49.689 --> 19:54.604
...and I want to be still feeling this now.

19:54.777 --> 19:57.735
I want to so, so bad.

19:59.281 --> 20:01.442
That's all I need to hear.

20:07.790 --> 20:08.950
[TIMER BEEPS]

20:09.291 --> 20:11.452
LUDWIG:
And time.

20:12.628 --> 20:13.788
This'll sting a bit.

20:14.338 --> 20:15.748
[SCREAMS]

20:16.257 --> 20:18.122
You fucking cunt.

20:18.300 --> 20:21.508
Gonna shove my fist up your ass,
and use you as a hand warmer.

20:22.138 --> 20:23.799
Shush, you're not helping.

20:24.598 --> 20:27.886
Please shut the fuck up and fix me.

20:28.060 --> 20:31.644
