20:45.453 --> 20:46.909
[GROANS]

20:50.166 --> 20:52.157
This will speed the healing.

20:52.334 --> 20:55.326
One in each buttock, one in each arm,
one in each temple.

20:55.504 --> 20:57.495
Six shots, four times a day.

20:57.673 --> 20:59.664
-For how long?
-Forever.

21:00.509 --> 21:02.010
For forever?

21:02.178 --> 21:04.544
I can get you a bulk discount
on the shots.

21:05.222 --> 21:08.180
[GROANS]

21:08.851 --> 21:10.842
Your brother
had some nasty food poisoning.

21:11.020 --> 21:12.510
His fever's down from 105...

21:12.688 --> 21:16.021
