21:20.029 --> 21:21.690
Will you tell her?

21:22.198 --> 21:25.281
Yeah, it's true.
Our family, we're naturally warm.

21:28.204 --> 21:31.367
-Huh. That's strange.
-See?

21:31.540 --> 21:33.326
I don't feel flush or nothing.

21:33.501 --> 21:35.708
So whatever it was,
I must have threw it all up.

21:36.629 --> 21:39.541
Can Ijust go home, please?

21:40.382 --> 21:44.091
Get changed.
I'll grab the discharge instructions.

21:44.887 --> 21:47.003
-Tommy. You sure you're okay?
TOMMY: Ain't a thing.

21:47.181 --> 21:49.297
I got no insurance.
I can't stay another day.

21:49.475 --> 21:53.218
-Tommy. That's not a reason.
-|'m fine. I swear, I'm good.

21:53.395 --> 21:57.013
You looked like you were two steps
from death's door. What happened to you?

21:57.191 --> 21:58.306
I don't know.

21:58.484 --> 22:02.193
I figured you'd be home late,
so Ijust took the full moon run on my own.

22:02.363 --> 22:04.570
