-Don't blame yourself.

22:14.750 --> 22:15.910
Wasn't you.

22:18.045 --> 22:19.376
[DOOR KNOCKS]

22:22.258 --> 22:24.749
Oh. Hey.

22:24.927 --> 22:26.417
SooMe.

22:35.604 --> 22:37.640
Your Majesty.

22:39.567 --> 22:41.353
